# diamondSpiral

- _diamondSpiral(n)_

Answer the first _n_ lattice coordinates of a counterclockwise diamond spiral.

_x_-coordinates of diamond spiral,
OEIS [A010751](https://oeis.org/A010751):

~~~spl svg=A oeis=A010751
65.diamondSpiral.column(1)
.scatterPlot
~~~

![](Help/Image/diamondSpiral-A.svg)

_y_-coordinates of diamond spiral,
OEIS [A305258](https://oeis.org/A305258):

~~~spl svg=B oeis=A305258
65.diamondSpiral.column(2)
.scatterPlot
~~~

![](Help/Image/diamondSpiral-B.svg)

~~~spl svg=C
65.diamondSpiral.pointLinePlot
~~~

![](Help/Image/diamondSpiral-C.svg)

* * *

See also: squareSpiral
